12_Gauge.help: You fire a shot from your 12 Gauge Shotgun, causing lethal damage to several enemies in a cone in front of you. There is also a chance for affected targets to be knocked down.
12_Gauge.shortHelp: Ranged (Cone), High DMG (Lethal), Chance for Knockdown (Foe)

Frag_Grenade.help: You throw a fragmentation grenade at a single target. This explodes on impact, throwing shrapnel that causes smashing and lethal damage. There is also a high chance that the concussive effect from the explosion will knock affected targets back.
Frag_Grenade.shortHelp: Ranged (Targeted AoE), Extreme DMG (Smashing/Lethal), Chance for Knockback (Foe)
